  "plot": [
    {
      "plot_summary": "The TARDIS arrives on the planet Skaro, where the First Doctor and his companions discover the Dalek City and the two indigenous races: the Daleks, armored mutant creatures, and the Thal humanoids. The Daleks are survivors of a devastating war with the Thals, who have since become pacifists. The Doctor and his friends become caught up in the struggle between the two races, and ultimately lead the Thals in an attack on the Dalek City, destroying the Daleks by cutting off their power supply."
